<h1>Grid</h1>
<p>Grid system.</p>



<h2>Base</h2>
<p>Basic wrapper and column classes. These can be modified as shown further down the page.</p>

<h3>Wrapper</h3>
{{#markdown}}
```html
<div class="grid">
    [...]
</div>
```
{{/markdown}}
<div class="spaced-sm milli">
    <div class="grid">
        <div class="col-4"><div class="example-col">.col-4</div></div> 
        <div class="col-4"><div class="example-col">.col-4</div></div> 
        <div class="col-4"><div class="example-col">.col-4</div></div> 
    </div>
</div>

<h3>Columns</h3>
{{#markdown}}
```html
<div class="grid">
    <div class="col-4">[...]</div>
</div>
```
{{/markdown}}
<div class="spaced-md milli">
